# Coding workflow prefrences

- Focus on the areas of code relevant to the task
- Do not touch code that is inrelated to the task
- Write thorough tests for all major functionality
- Avoid major changes to the patterns and architecture of how a feature works, after it has shown to work well, unless sxplicitly instructed
